data.description: Welcome to 16724 Lantana Dr., Primera, TX 78552! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home is a true gem, offering 2,506 square feet of spacious living on a generous .81-acre lot. As you approach this home, you'll be immediately captivated by its unique brick siding, located in a quiet and peaceful neighborhood. The garage side entrance provides ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. Inside, you'll find tasteful tile flooring throughout, providing a clean and elegant backdrop for your personal style along with updated light fixtures and other upgrades. Each room has access to restrooms and ample closets. The half bath features inside and outside entrances which are very convenient for your get-togethers. The roof and A/C units are 1.5 years old, offering peace of mind and protection. This property has a well-water irrigation system for the lawn, keeping your green spaces lush and vibrant year-round. Come see this property and make it yours today, bring an offer!!
